'''高铼酸钕'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Nd(ReO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>，存在无水物和四水合物<ref>Varfolomeev, M. B.; Plyushchev, V. E.; Rybakov, K. A. Monoclinic modification of neodymium perrhenate tetrahydrate. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1967. 12 (5): 1410-1411. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref><ref>Mashonkin, V. P.; Ilyukhin, V. V.; Varfolomeev, M. B. Structure of rhombic rare earth perrhenate tetrahydrates RE(ReO4)​3.4H2O (RE = praseodymium-​dysprosium). ''Koordinatsionnaya Khimiya'', 1977. 3 (7): 1014-1019. ISSN: 0132-344X.</ref>。它可由过量的[[氧化钕|氧化钕]]和240 g/L的[[高铼酸|高铼酸]]溶液反应得到。<ref>Plyushchev, V. E.; Amosov, V. M.; Varfolomeev, M. B. Synthesis and certain properties of lower crystallohydrates of yttrium, lanthanum, and lanthanoid perrhenates. ''Doklady Akademii Nauk SSSR'', 1963. 150 (1): 105-108. ISSN: 0002-3264.</ref>在其溶液中可以观测到NdReO<sub>4</sub><sup>2+</sup>和Nd(ReO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>，稳定常数分别为16.5和23.6。<ref>Petrov, K. I.; Orlin, N. A.; Plyushchev, V. E. Neodymium perrhenate complexes studied by a spectrographic method. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1969. 14 (10): 2739-2742. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

高铼酸钕和NdRe<sub>2</sub>在高温下反应，可以制得Nd<sub>4</sub>Re<sub>6</sub>O<sub>19</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=147|issue=1|language=en|date=1999-10|pages=218–228|doi=10.1006/jssc.1999.8237|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459699982373|title=Preparation, Crystal Structures, and Properties of Rhenates with Multiple Re–Re Bonds: Ln2ReO5 (Ln=Sm, Eu, Gd), Ln3Re2O9 (Ln=Pr, Nd, Sm), and Ln4Re6O19 (Ln=La–Nd)|accessdate=2020-08-30|author=Wolfgang Jeitschko, Dieter H Heumannskämper, Marietta S Schriewer-Pöttgen, Ute Ch Rodewald|archive-date=2018-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608082045/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459699982373|dead-url=no}}</ref>

